.Vt struct audit_plugin
has the following fields:
.Bl -tag -width 4n
.It Fa type
The
.Fa type
field should always be set to
.Dv SUDO_IO_PLUGIN .
.It Fa version
The
.Fa version
field should be set to
.Dv SUDO_API_VERSION .
.Pp
This allows
.Nm sudo
to determine the API version the plugin was
built against.
.It Fa open
